@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Gruer's Story";
}

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <div class="warm-card text-center mb-5">
                <i class="bi bi-egg-fried display-1 text-warm"></i>
                <h1 class="display-4 mt-3">Gruer's Story</h1>
                <div class="honey-accent mx-auto"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warm-card">
                <div class="story-text">
                    <p>Gruer's eyes drift closed for a moment, his weathered face softening as he pictures it.</p>
                    
                    <p>When he opens them, they are bright with vision.</p>
                    
                    <p>"Signore, I have dreamed of this shop for decades. But never—" he pauses, searching for words, "—never like this."</p>
                    
                    <p>He begins to pace, his hands gesturing as he speaks.</p>
                    
                    <p>"First, the space. It should be warm—warm like the sun on a spring morning, warm like the ovens I've tended for years. Wood and stone, soft lighting, tables that invite you to stay."</p>
                    
                    <p>He stops, looking at you.</p>
                    
                    <p>"But also... otherworldly. A hint of the magic that brought me here. Glowing accents—soft gold, gentle amber. Plants from your yard, flowers that bloom in colors I've never seen."</p>
                    
                    <p>"A place that feels like home, but also like a dream."</p>
                    
                    <div class="honey-accent my-4"></div>
                    
                    <p class="fst-italic text-center">"This is what I imagine, signore. A place of warmth and wonder. A place where ordinary people can taste other worlds. A place where every bite tells a story."</p>
                    
                    <div class="honey-accent my-4"></div>
                    
                    <p class="text-end">— Gruer, Master Baker</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>